  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/9d187bfe7e051afaa437c75c6169edc9.poster.avif?t=1719560174\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/9d187bfe7e051afaa437c75c6169edc9.webm?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/9d187bfe7e051afaa437c75c6169edc9.mp4?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get ready to experience racing like never before. Use your epic driving skills and use all the powerups to cross first in the finish line. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/0adc8aeffaafdf6e710920b15f3021c7.poster.avif?t=1719560174\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/0adc8aeffaafdf6e710920b15f3021c7.webm?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/0adc8aeffaafdf6e710920b15f3021c7.mp4?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/dac0668b600f2b6bee7b9c328578aa0d.poster.avif?t=1719560174\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/dac0668b600f2b6bee7b9c328578aa0d.webm?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/dac0668b600f2b6bee7b9c328578aa0d.mp4?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Compete in 4 different game modes</strong> <br>Multiplayer, Championship, Arcade and Time Trial. <br>Cross-Platform Multiplayer Support<br>Compete against others on the Leaderboards<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/b55c8ce3c249a124547b9c0ef99351bc.poster.avif?t=1719560174\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/b55c8ce3c249a124547b9c0ef99351bc.webm?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/b55c8ce3c249a124547b9c0ef99351bc.mp4?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Cars, Cars, Cars...</strong><br>Over 8 different cars to choose from, ranging from Sports cars to Vintage cars. <br>Customize your cars with new Skins, Toppers and Boosters. <br>Collect coins to upgrade your cars to be the best they can be.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/2cb511fc655acfeb3a49c7087d07cb8e.poster.avif?t=1719560174\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/2cb511fc655acfeb3a49c7087d07cb8e.webm?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902830/extras/2cb511fc655acfeb3a49c7087d07cb8e.mp4?t=1719560174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Vroom Vroom Vroom...</strong><br>9 different tracks, each have their own sets of obstacles and challenges for you to overcome and emerge victorious.<br>8 Different Championships to playthrough<br>Play through all the levels in arcade mode and time trial<br><br>While you're racing watch out for the opponents who like to go rogue and push you off the edges of the track.<br><br>ABOUT US<br>Smash Game Studios is an Indie Game company focused on creating compelling experience for Mobile, PC and New Emerging Platforms. We're best known for our games The Last Train.",
